text:
@JoeBiden COVID-19 = the new 1918-H1N1

This is not good.

1918-H1N1 pandemic killed 675,000 people from a U.S. population of 103,000,000.

COVID-19 must kill 3,000,000 Americans to match.

Trump both refused WHO tests on February 1st and wrecked pandemic response in 2018.

The latter: https://t.co/dLOlLlanj7
